snippet.textDisplay:
This is a cool video and concept to watch but it would've been nice of there was more variety in the clothes. Like obviously it's not her style to have colours or interesting prints but if this is meant to be a video showcasing how a personal shopper works then I don't think we can really see the full spectrum of possibility for a personal online shopper if the only choices are black and white dresses and leggings.
There's not much point in spending money on a stylist to give you a black shirt and grey leggings, something more adventurous would be exciting.
